Package.description: FinancialForce ClickLink is a point and click tool built on the Force.com platform that allows you to transform data from one object into another. You can take any object as a source, transform the data and populate any other target object. To use FinancialForce ClickLink, each user must be assigned an FFA, PSA, HCM or SCM license.
